'''结肠癌缺失蛋白'''（Deleted in Colorectal Carcinoma,<ref>[http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?Db=gene&Cmd=ShowDetailView&TermToSearch=1630&ordinalpos=1&itool=EntrezSystem2.PEntrez.Gene.Gene_ResultsPanel.Gene_RVDocSum NCBI Website for DCC]</ref> DCC）是一种由DCC基因编码的人类蛋白质。由于1990年在一项结肠癌研究中发现该蛋白,<ref name=Fearon>{{cite journal |author=Fearon ER, Cho KR, Nigro JM, ''et al.'' |title=Identification of a chromosome 18q gene that is altered in colorectal cancers |journal=Science |volume=247 |issue=4938 |pages=49–56 |pmid=2294591 |url=http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=2294591 |doi=10.1126/science.2294591|date=January 1990}}</ref> 所以命名为结肠癌缺失蛋白。

关于结肠癌缺失蛋白作用于[[肿瘤抑制基因|肿瘤抑制]]研究有许多争议，该蛋白还是众所周知的针对netrin-1反应的[[轴突导向|轴突导向]][[受体|受体]]。<ref name="pmid17449433">{{cite journal | author = Bernet A, Mehlen P | title = Dependence receptors: when apoptosis controls tumor progression | journal = Bull Cancer | volume = 94 | issue = 4 | pages = E12–7 | pmid = 17449433 | doi = | url = http://www.john-libbey-eurotext.fr/medline.md?issn=0007-4551&vol=94&iss=4&page=E12 | issn = |date=April 2007}}</ref>

